kept popping up in your sister's dream.

22
00:02:38,625 --> 00:02:40,044
Tell me about it.

23
00:02:41,545 --> 00:02:43,505
You have no idea how relieved I am.

24
00:02:45,966 --> 00:02:47,009
-Anyway, good day.
-You too.

25
