159
00:16:17,610 --> 00:16:19,529
so you should at least drink like a boss.

160
00:16:21,197 --> 00:16:25,160
<i>Bloodshot eyes, chapped lips,
and a yellow complexion.</i>

161
00:16:25,243 --> 00:16:26,619
