218
00:19:32,793 --> 00:19:35,379
Do you have any idea
how much pressure I'm under?

219
00:19:35,463 --> 00:19:37,298
I need something to report
to the higher-ups.

220
00:19:37,381 --> 00:19:38,883
And you do.

221
00:19:38,966 --> 00:19:40,676
